quran[269]{c,v,t}:
  18,75,"[Khadiru] wi'i: \"Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaake muñal wonndugol e an"
  18,76,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Si mi lanndike ma gaayi huunde ɓaawo ɗii, haray wata a wonndino e an, gomɗii a timminii nganto e an"
  18,77,"Ɓe yahi haa ɓe yaltiti e yimɓe saare, ɓe ɗaɓɓiri ɓe ñaametee ɓe salii wernude ɓe, ɓe tawi e nder mayre maadi faalaa fukkaade [Khadiru] o darnindi , o [Muusaa] maaki: \"Sinno a yiɗuno a ƴettayno njoddi e ɗun"
  18,78,"[Khadiru] maaki: \"Ko ɗum woni seedigal hakku- nde an e ma'a, aray mi yiito maa firo kon ko a hattananooka munñaade e dow mun"
  18,79,"Si ko laana kan, ka laatanike miskineeɓe gollo- ɓe ka maayo, mi faalaa aybinnde ka, hari laatike ɓaawo maɓɓe lamɗo himo nannga kala laana o jaɓta"
  18,80,"Si ko suka on mawɓe makko ɓen wonii gomɗimɓe , men huli wata o fawu ɓe bewre e keeferaaku"
  18,81,Men faalaa nde Joomi maɓɓe waɗtitanta ɓe ɓurɗo mo moƴƴude laaɓuɗo e ɓurɗo ɓattaade yurmeende
  18,82,"Si ko maadi ndin, ndi laatanino sukaaɓe ɗiɗo wonɗuɓe ka saare, laatii ley mayri ngalu maɓɓe kamɓe ɗiɗo, hari baaba maɓɓe laatinoke moƴƴo, Joomi maaɗa Faalaa nde ɓe yottotoo sagatalaaku maɓɓe, O yaltina ngalu maɓɓe ngun [ɗum] ko Yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa, mi waɗiraali ɗum e yamirooree an, ɗum ko firo kon ko a hattanaali munñaade e dow mun"
  18,83,"Hiɓe fa'umaa lanndaade fii Julqarnayni, maaku: \"Aray mi jannga e taweede mon e ɗun janta"
  18,84,"Menen, Men weeɓinanno mo ka leydi, Men Okki mo immorde e kala huunde sabu"
  18,85,O jokki sabu
  18,86,"Haa nde o yottinoo ka mutirde naange ngen o tawi hinge muta e loope ɓaleeje, o tawi ton yimɓe : Men wi'i: \"Ko an yo jom galaaɗi ɗiɗi, ko si a leptay maaɗun si a jogitoto e maɓɓe ko moƴƴi"
  18,87,"O wi'i: Si tawii ko on tooñuɗo aray men lepta mo, refti o ruttee ka Joomi makko O lepta mo lepte añiiɗe"
  18,88,"Si tawii ko on gomɗinɗo o golli ko moƴƴi no woodani mo njoɓdi moƴƴiri ndin, aray Men wi'ana mo e fiyaake Amen on neweende"
  18,89,Refti o jokki laawol
  18,90,"Haa nde o yottinoo ka ƴellitorde naange ngen, o tawi hinge ƴellitoo e dow yimɓe, Men waɗanaali ɓe gaanin magge heedo"
  18,91,"Ko wano nii, gomɗii Men huɓindike ko woni kon ka makko e ganndal. @Corrected"
  18,92,Refti o jokki laawol
  18,93,Haa nde o yottinoo hakkunde heedooji ɗin ɗiɗio tawi gaanin majji yimɓe ɓe ɗeɓataa faamude konngol
  18,94,"Ɓe wi'i: \"Ko an Julqarnayni, pellet, Yaajuuja e Maajuuja ko bonnooɓe ka leydi. Enee, men waɗante ngeenaari fii yo a waɗu hakkunde amen e maɓɓe heedo"
  18,95,"O wi'i: \"Ko Joomi am weeɓinani lan kon ɓuri moƴƴude, walliree lan doole mi waɗa hakkunde mo'on e maɓɓe heedo"
  18,96,"Addanee lam kunte njamɗe haa nde o feppi- ndirnoo hakkunde naɗe ɗen ɗiɗi, o wi'i: \"Wifee haa nde o waɗunoo ɗum yiite, o wi'i: addanee lam sila mi wancina e dow mun"
  18,97,"Ɓe hattantaake ƴellitagol ndi, ɓe hattantaake kadi yulugol ndi"
  18,98,"O wi'i: ɗum ɗoo ko Yurmeende immornde e Joomi am, si Fodoore Joomi am nden arii O waɗay [heedo] ngon ɗiggungo, Fodoore Joomi am nden laatike ko nde Goonga"
  18,99,"Men ɗala yoga e maɓɓe nden ñalnde no yolloo e yoga, wuttaa ka allaadu Men mooɓa ɓe mooɓudee"
  18,100,Men weeɓitanay(holliray) Jahannama nden ñannde yedduɓe ɓen weeɓitugol=holllirgol
  18,101,"Ɓen ɓe gite mun laatii e wirngallo gaayi janta An, ɓe laatiɓe hattantaake nanugol"
  18,102,"Enee, ɓen yedduɓe sikku ɓe jogoto jeyaaɓe Am ɓen gaanin Am, Menen Men heblanii Jahannama on fii yedduɓeɓen wona werde. @Corrected"
  18,103,"Maaku: \"Taw si men hupitay on fii ɓurɓe hayrude(pertude) golle"
  18,104,Ko ɓen ɓe golle mun yeebii ka ngurdan aduna hara kamɓe hiɓe sikka hiɓe moƴƴinnde golle
  18,105,"Ko ɓen woni yedduɓe Aayeeje Joomi maɓɓe ɗen e hawroygol e Makko, golle maɓɓe ɗen bone Men ñiiɓinantaaɓe Ñalnde Darngal Ɓetu"
  18,106,"Jahannama ko ɗun woni njoɓdi maɓɓe, sabu ko ɓe yeddi kon ɓe jogitii Aayeeje Am ɗen e Nulaaɓe Am ɓen jalkitde"
  18,107,"Pellet, ɓen gomɗimɓe ɓe golli moƴƴi ɗin laatanto ɓe Aljannaaji Firdawsi Werdi(jipporde)"
  18,108,"Ko ɓe duumotooɓe nder ton, ɓe ɗaɓɓataa gaayi makko waylitorde"
  18,109,"Maaku: \"Sinno maayo ngo laatino ndawa fii Daaluyeeji Joomi am ɗin, maayo ngon re'ayno ko adii nde re'ata Daaluyeeji Joomi am ɗin, sinno Men addii yeru maggo e ɓeydude"
  18,110,"Maaku: \"Pellet min, ko mi ɓanndinnke yeru mon, no wahayineede e am. Pellet, Reweteeɗo mon On ko Reweteeɗo Gooto, kala jortiiɗo hawroyde e Joomi makko yo o gollu golle moƴƴe wata o kafidu e dewal Joomi makko hay e gooto"
  19,1,Kaaf Haa Yaa ayiin saad
  19,2,Jaŋta Yurmeende Joomi maaɗa jeyaaɗo Makko on Jakariyaa
  19,3,Tuma nde O noddunoo Joom makko noddaannu suuɗiindu
  19,4,"O maaki: \"Jooma, min dey ƴi'e ɗen lo'ii e am hoore nden lewndii puri, mi laataaki non ɗawaaɗo ka toragol Ma Jooma"
  19,5,"Min dey mi hulii lontotooɓe ɓen ɓaawo am, suddiiɗo am on laatike dimaro okkam immorde ka Maaɗa ɓiɗɗo"
  19,6,"O rona lam, o rona kadi e ɓeynguure Yaaquuba nden waɗaa mo Joomi weltoraaɗo"
  19,7,Ko an yo Jakariyaa Menen Men weltinirii ma suka innde makko ko Yahyaa Men waɗanaali mo ko adii tokoraajo
  19,8,"O maaki: \"Jooma ko honno laatoranta lam suka sonnaajo am on laatike dimaro min kadi mi yottike e nayewu yooruɗo tere"
  19,9,"[Malaa'ikaajo on] wi'i: \"Ko nii Joomi maaɗa Daaliri: Ɗum no neewii e Am gomɗii Mi Tagiino ma ko adii, hari a laataaki huunde"
  19,10,"O maaki: \"Jooma waɗanam Maande\". O Daali: \"Maande maaɗa nden ko wata a wowlidu e yimɓe ɓen jemmaaji tati fotondirɗi"
  19,11,"O yalti hakkunde yimɓe makko ɓen immorde ka ganngunal o joopii faande e maɓɓe, ɗum woni subunhinee bimmbi e kiikiiɗe"
  19,12,"Ko an yo Yahyaa nanngir deftere nden doole, Men Okki mo Ñeeñal ko o suka"
  19,13,"E Yurmeende immorde ka Amen ko o laaɓuɗo o laatike huloowo [Alla]"
  19,14,Ko o ɗigganɗo jibimɓe mo ɓen o wanaali ndunndarankeejo ngeddo
  19,15,Kisiyee e makko ñalnde o jibinaa e ñalnde o maayata e Ñalnde o immintintee ko o wuuruɗo
  19,16,"Jaŋto ka Deftere Mariyama tuma nde o woɗɗitinoo immorde e yimɓe makko ɓen [o yaari] e nokkuure funnaangeyankoore"
  19,17,"O jogitii gaanin maɓɓe wirngallo, Men Nuli e makko Ruuhu Amen o nanndintinanii mo e ɓanndinke fotondirɗo"
  19,18,"O maaki: min mi moolorii Yurmeteeɗo On immorde e maaɗa si tawii a laatike ko a kulo [Alla]"
  19,19,"O wi'i: \"Pellet, min ko mi Nulaaɗo Joomi maaɗa fii yo mi okke suka laaɓuɗo"
  19,20,"O wi'i: \"Ko honno laatoranta lam suka hara ɓanndinke meemaali lam mi laataaki kadi jeenoowo(pijoowo)"
  19,21,"O wi'i: \"ko nii Joomi maaɗa Daaliri: \"Ɗum no newii e Am e fii yo Men waɗu mo Maande fii yimɓe ɓen e Yurmeende immornde e Amen ɗum laatike fiyaake Ñaawaaɗo"
  19,22,"O roondii mo, o pottidodi e makko e nokkuure woɗɗitiinde"
  19,23,"Ŋata(qatwere) on fiɗi mo e jullere tamarohi, o wi'i: \"Ee hara nun mi maayuno ko adii ɗum mi laatoo huunde yejjitaande"
  19,24,"O noddi mo immorde e ley makki, [o wi'i] wata a suno gomɗii Joomi maaɗa waɗii ley maaɗa caangol"
  19,25,Yeƴu(dimmbu) faade e maaɗa jullere tamarohi kin nde liɓa e maaɗa ɓennduɗe teɓeteeɗe
  19,26,"Ñaamu yaraa ɓuɓɓinaa gite, si a yi'ii goɗɗo immorde e ɓanndinke wi'u: \"Min dey mi takkanii Hinnorante(jurmotooɗo korka mi wowlidata e neɗɗanke hannde)"
  19,27,"O radi e makko ka yimɓe makko, himo tammbii mo ɓe wi'i: \"Ko an yo Mariyama gomɗii a addii huunde hawnii nde"
  19,28,Ko an yo banndiraawo Haaruuna baaba maa laatanooki neɗɗo bonɗo neene maaɗa kadi laataaki jeenoowo=jinoowo
  19,29,"[Mariyama] joopii e makko, ɓe wi'i:\"Ko honno men yewtirta e on sanfaajo wonɗo e woofordu(liir) gondo e tiiggu"
  19,30,"[Iisaa] maaki: \"Min dey ko mi jeyaaɗo Alla O Okkii lam Deftere nden O Waɗii lam Annabaajo"
  19,31,"O Waɗi lam Barkinaaɗo nokku kala ka mi woni, O Wasiyii lam Julde nden e Jakka on fodde miɗo wuuri"
  19,32,"Ko mi ɗigganɗo yumma am, O waɗaali lam ndunndarankeejo malkisaaɗo"
  19,33,Kisiyee on wonii e am ñalnde mi jibinaa e ñal- nde mi maayata e Ñalnde mi immintintee ko mi wuuruɗo
  19,34,On ko Iisaa geɗal Mariyama Daalol Goongawol ngol hiɓe sikkitoo fii mu'un
  19,35,"Haananaa Alla nde O jogitotoo ɓiɗɗo Senayee wonanii Mo, si O Ñaawii fiyaake O Daalanay mo tun: \"Wonu\" o wona"
  19,36,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon, Rewee Mo. Ko ɗum woni Laawol Focciingol"
  19,37,"Feddeeji ɗin luutondiri hakkunde majji, bone wonanii ɓen yedduɓe seedagol Ñalaande Mawnde"
  19,38,"Kaawee ko nanirta yi'ira wa maɓɓe Ñalnde ɓe aroyta e Amen, kono tooñooɓe ɓen hannde hiɓe e nder majjere ɓanngunde"
  19,39,"Hulɓinir ɓe Ñalnde Nimse, tuma nde fiyaake on ñaawaa hara kamɓe hiɓe e nder welsindaare hara ɓe gomɗinaa"
  19,40,"Menen Men ronay leydi ndin e ɓen wonuɓe e dow mayri, ko ka Amen ɓe ruttetee"
  19,41,"Jaŋto ka Deftere Ibraahiima, pellet, kanko o laatino Goonguɗo Annabaajo"
  19,42,"Tuma nde o maakannoo bem makko: \"Ko an yo baaba ko honɗun rewantaa kon ko nanataa yi'ataa hara duncantaa ma hay e huunde"
  19,43,"Ko an yo baaba min dey gomɗii arii lam immorde e Ganndal kon ko araali e maaɗa, jokkam mi fewne e Laawol Focciingol"
  19,44,"Ko an yo baaba, wata a rewu Seytaane, pellet, Seytaane laatike yedduɗo Hinnorante"
  19,45,"Ko an yo baaba, min dey miɗo huli wta meeme Lepte immorde ka Hinnorante laatanoɗaa Seytaane giɗo"
  19,46,"[Baaba makko] wi'i: \"Enee, an a añu reweteeɗi am ɗin nee Ibraahiima, pellet, si a accaali mi rajmete selam dummunne [juutuɗo]"
  19,47,"[Ibraahiima] maaki: \"Kisal e maaɗa aray mi insinanomaa ka Joomi am, pellet, Konko O Laatike Newaniiɗo lam"
  19,48,"Mi martoo(deestoo) on e kon ko rewoton gaanin Alla, mi toroo Joomi am no gasa mi wonataa tampirɗo toragol Joomi am"
  19,49,"Tuma nde o martinoo(deestinoo) ɓe e ko ɓe rewata kon gaanin Alla, Men Okki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba kala [gooto e maɓɓe] Men waɗi [mo] Annabaajo"
  19,50,"Men Okki ɓe immorde e Yurmeende Amen, Men waɗani ɓe ɗenngal goonga toowungal"
  19,51,"Jaŋto ka Deftere Muusaa, pellet, kanko o laatinoke laɓɓinɗo o laatinoke kadi Nulaaɗo Annabaajo"
  19,52,"Men noddi mo ka senngo ñaamo [fello] Tuuri Men ɓattini mo gunndeteeɗo"
  19,53,Men Okki mo immorde e Yurmeende Amen musiɗɗo makko on Haaruuna Annabaajo
  19,54,"Jaŋto ka Deftere Ismaa'iila, pellet, kanko o laatinoke Goonguɗo fodoore o laatinoke kadi Nulaaɗo Annabaajo"
  19,55,"O laatino himo yamira yimɓe makko ɓen Julde e Jakka on, o laatino kadi Weltoraaɗo ka Joomi makko"
  19,56,"Jaŋto ka Deftere Idriisa, pellet, kanko o laatino Goonguɗo Annabaajo"
  19,57,Men ɓanti mo e nokkuure Toowunde
  19,58,"Ko ɓen woni ɓen, ɓe Alla Neemini e dow mu'un immorde e Annabaaɓe ka geɗal ɓebibbe Aadama e ɓen ɓe Men waɗɗinnoo wonndude e Nuuhu e geɗalɓe Ibraahiima e Israa'iila e ɓen ɓe Men Fewni Men Suɓii si janngaama e dow maɓɓe Aayeeje Hinnorante ɓe fukko koɓe sujjooɓe e wullooɓe. @Corrected"
  19,59,"Lontii ɓaawo maɓɓe lontotooɓe, ɓe yeebi Julde nden ɓe jokki welnuruuji ɗin aray ɓe hawroya e bone"
  19,60,"Si wanaa on tuubuɗo o gomɗini o golli ko moƴƴi, ɓen ɗon ɓe naatay Aljanna on ɓe tooñiroy- taake hay e huunde"
  19,61,"Aljannaaji Adan ɗin ɗi Hinnorante On Fodi jeyaaɓe Makko ɓen e birnagal, pellet Kanko, Fodoore Makko nden laatike ko aroore"
  19,62,"Ɓe nanataa nder ton rayrayti si wonaa kisiyee, no woodani ɓe arsike maɓɓe on nder ton bimmbi e kiikiiɗe"
  19,63,"On Aljanna mo Men Roninta immorde e jeyaaɓe Amen ɓen, on laatiiɗo kulo [Alla]"
  19,64,"Men jippotaako si wanaa e Yamaruyee Joomi maaɗa, no woodani Mo ko woni kon hedde yeeso amen e ko woni kon ɓaawo amen e ko woni kon hakkunde ɗum, Joomi maaɗa laataaki yejjitoowo"
  19,65,"Jooma kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, Rewu mo monñitor Dewal Makko. Taw si hiɗa anndani Mo tokoraajo"
  19,66,"Neɗɗanke on no wi'a: \"Eyoo, e jaka si mi maai aroyay ka mi yaltinee tawa ko mi wuuruɗo"
  19,67,"Enee, neɗɗanke on annditaali Menen Men Tagiino mo ko adii, hari o wonaali hay e huunde"
  19,68,"Mi woondirii Joomi maaɗa Men mooɓay ɓe sanne e Seytanuuji ɗin, refti Men adda ɓe sara Jahannama ko ɓe jiccii ɓe"
  19,69,Refti Men ɗoofa immorde e kala fedde ko hommbo e maɓɓe ɓurnoo saɗtude dartagol e dow Hinnorante On
  19,70,Refti ko Menen Anndi ɓen ɓurɓe hanndude e sumugol e magge
  19,71,"Alaa hay e gooto e mo'on si wanaa o joloyay e magge, ɗum laatike e dow Joomi maaɗa ko Ñaawaaɗum Tentinaa"
  19,72,"Refti Men ndannda ɓen hulunooɓe [Alla] Men ɗala tooñooɓe ɓen ko ɓe jicciiɓe nder ton"
  19,73,"Si janngaama e taweede maɓɓe Aayeeje Amen Ɓannguɗe ɗen; yedduɓe ɓen wi'ana gom- ɗimɓe ɓen: \"Ko honnde e feddeeji ɗin ɗiɗi ɓuri moƴƴude darnde ɓuri moƴƴude kadi mbatu"
  19,74,Heewii ko Men halki ado maɓɓe immorde e gire tawi ko kamɓe ɓuri fotude mirannji suudu e mbaadi
  19,75,"Maaku: \"On laatiiɗo e nder majjere nden yo Hinnorante fontan mo fontudee, haa si ɓe yi'ii ko ɓe fodaa kon, si tawii ko lepte ɗen maa si ko Darngal ngal, aray ɓe annda on m bonuɗo nukkuure e ɓurɗo lo'ude konu"
  19,76,"Alla no ɓeydana ɓen feewuɓe Peewal, Moƴƴi heddotooɗi ɗin ɓuri moƴƴude mbarjaari ka Joomi maaɗa ɓuri moƴƴude kadi ruttorde"
  19,77,"Enee, a yi'ii on yedduɗo Aayeeje Amen ɗen, o wi'i: \"Maatun mi okkee jawdi e ɓiɗɗo"
  19,78,"Enee o ƴelliti e ko wirnii kon, kaa jogiti ka Hinnorante Aadi"
  19,79,"Wanaa non, aray Men winnda ko o wi'ata kon Men ɓeydana mo immorde e Lepte ɗen ɓeydude"
  19,80,"Men Rona mo e ko o wi'ata kon, o ara e Amen ko o weddiiɗo(gooto)"
  19,81,Ɓe jogitii gaanin Alla reweteeɗi fii yo ɗi laatano ɓe teddungal. @Corrected
  19,82,"Wonaa non, maɓe yedda rewugolɓe ngol, ɓe laatanoo ɓe ayɓe"
  19,83,Enee a yi'aali Menen Men Nulii Seytanuuji e dow yedduɓe ɓen hiɗi ƴuuna ɓe ƴuunudee
  19,84,"Wata a hawjan ɓe, pellat, limonayɓebe limugol"
  19,85,"Ñalnde Men mooɓoyta hulooɓe [Alla] ɓen ka Hinnorante Teddinaaɓe"
  19,86,Men sogga bomɓe ɓen haa ka Jahannama ko ɓe jolooɓe
  19,87,Ɓe maraa tefoore nden si wanaa on jogitiiɗo ka Hinnorante Aadi
  19,88,"Ɓe wi'i: \"Hinnorante jogitike ɓiɗɗo"
  19,89,Gomɗii on addii huunde pankarɗii nde. @Corrected
  19,90,Kammuuli ɗin no do'a(ɗesa) seekaade immorde e ɗum leydi ndin feera pelle ɗen uuya fii unagol
  19,91,fii ɓe noddanii Hinnorante ɓiɗɗo
  19,92,Haananaa Hinnorante nde O jogitotoo ɓiɗɗo. @Corrected
  19,93,Alaa wonɗo ka kammuuli e ka leydi si wanaa o aray ka Hinnorante hombo woni jeyaaɗo
  19,94,Gomɗii O moftii ɓe O limii ɓe kadi e limugol. @Corrected
  19,95,"[Gooto] Kala e maɓɓe aray Mo Ñalnde Darngal ko o woddiiɗo(teeldɗo)"
  19,96,"Pellet, ɓen gomɗimɓe golli ko moƴƴi kon aray ka Hinnorante waɗanaɓe Giggol"
  19,97,"Anndu ko Men newiniri nde ka ɗenngal maaɗa; ko fii yo a weltinir nde hulooɓe [Alla] ɓen jertiniraa nde yimɓe saɗtuɓe wennje"
  19,98,"Heewii ko Men halki ado maɓɓe e gire taw si hiɗa so'a e maɓɓe immorde e goɗɗo, maa hiɗa nana ɓe hito"
  20,1,Taa Haa
  20,2,Men Telliniraali Alqur'aanaare nden e maaɗa fii yo a tampu
  20,3,"Si wonaa waaju wonannde on huloowo [Alla]"
  20,4,Ko Jippinaande immorde e On Taguɗo leydi ndin e kammuuli toowuɗi ɗin
  20,5,Hinnorante On O fotii ka dow Arsi kin. @Corrected
  20,6,No woodani Mo ko woni kon e kammuuli ɗin e ko woni kon e leydi nden e ko wini kon hakkunde majji kannji ɗiɗi e ko woni kon ka ley leydi
  20,7,"Si a fenñinii konngol ngol, pellet, Kanko hiMo Anndi gunndoo on e ko o suuɗi"
  20,8,"Alla reweteeɗo alaa si wanaa Kanko, no woodani Mo Inɗe Moƴƴe ɗen"
  20,9,taw si arii e maaɗa Yewtere fii Muusaa
  20,10,"Tuma nde o yi'unoo yiite, o wi'ani ɓeynguure makko nden: \"Ñiiɓee, min dey mi haynike jaynge bela-jo'o mi addanay on immorde e magge docotal maaɗum mi tawa ka [moggo] yiite tinndinoowo"
  20,11,"Tuma nde o arunoo e magge o noddaa; \"ko an yo Muusaa"
  20,12,"[Alla Daalano mo] Min dey ko Min Woni Joomi maaɗa solu paɗe maa ɗen; pellet an, hiɗa ka aynde(caatngol) Tuwaa Laɓɓinaande(seninangol)"
  20,13,Min Mi Suɓike ma Jento ko wonaa Wahyineede kon
  20,14,"Pellet, ko Min Woni Alla reweteeɗo alaa si wonaa Min Rewam; ñiiɓir e Julde nden fii Annditugol lam"
  20,15,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko aroowal Miɗo ɗeɓa suuɗude ngal fii yoɓe kala wonkii ko ki huuwi kon"
  20,16,Wata faddo ma e gaayi maggal on mo gom- ɗinaa ngal o jokki mbeleeɗe makko o halkii
  20,17,Ko honɗum woni ka ñaamo maaɗa an Muusaa
  20,18,"O maaki: \"Ndun ko tuggordu am miɗo tuggoo ndu miɗo liwtirana ndu dammi am ɗin, miɗo mari kadi haajuuji goo e mayru"
  20,19,"O Daali: \"Liɓu ndu, an Muusaa"
  20,20,"O liɓi ndu, tawi kayru ko ndu mboddi wonundi yahude"
  20,21,"O Daali: \"Nanngu ndu wata a hulu Men artiray ndu e mbaadi mayru araniri ndin"
  20,22,Ukku junngo maaɗa ngon ka nder jiiba maa; ngo yaltay ko ngo raneewo ko aldaa e bone ɗum ko Aaya goo
  20,23,Fii yo Men hollle immorde e Aayeeje Amen Mawɗe ɗen
  20,24,"Yahu ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o bewi"
  20,25,"O maaki: \"Jooma Yanñanam ɓernde am nden"
  20,26,Newinanaa lam fiyaake am on
  20,27,Firtaa finnde nden ka ɗenngal am
  20,28,Fii yo ɓe faamu konngol am ngol
  20,29,Waɗanaa lam ballo jeyaaɗo ka ɓeynguure am
  20,30,"[Hara ko] Haaruuna musiɗɗo am on"
  20,31,Semmbinir mo darnde am
  20,32,Tawnaa mo e nder fiyaake am on
  20,33,Fii yo men Senine ko ɗuuɗi
  20,34,Men jaŋtoMaa ko ɗuuɗi
  20,35,"Pellet, An A Wonii Humpitiiɗo Men"
  20,36,"O Daali: \"Gomɗii a okkaama toraare maaɗa nden an Muusaa"
  20,37,Gomɗii Men Neeminiino ma e laawol goo
  20,38,Tuma nde Men Wahayinnoo faade e yumma maa ko Wahayinaa kon
  20,39,"[Men Daali] Bugo mo ka nder hontoore bugoɗaa nden kadi ka nder diidere, yo diidere nden kadi bugoyo mo ka fonngo; ƴetta mo gaño Am e gaño makko, Mi werlii e maaɗa Giggol immorde ka Am e fii yo a ne'e e dow ndenka Am"
  20,40,"Tuma nde banndiraawo maaɗa on yahaynoo; o wi'a: \"Enee, yo mi tinndin on e on mo no ne'a mo?\" Men artirmaa ka yumma maaɗa fii yo gite makko ɗen ɓuuɓu hara o sunaaki. Waruɗaa wonkii Men danndumaa immorde e saɗteende nden, Men jarribimaa jarrabuyeeje ñiiɓuɗaa duuɓi ka yimɓe Madyana refti aruɗaa ka fodoore ko an yo Muusaa"
  20,41,Mi Suɓimaa fii hoore-Am
  20,42,Yahu an e musiɗɗo maa on wonndude e Aayeeje Am ɗen wata on derfu e jaŋtagol Lam
  20,43,"Yahee ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o bewi"
  20,44,Wi'anee mo konngol newiingol bela-jo'o kanko o waajitoto maaɗum o hula
  20,45,"Ɓe maaki: \"Joomi amen, menen dey meɗen huli nde murtata e hoore amen maa nde o bewata"
  20,46,"O Daali: \"Wata on hulu, pellet, Min Miɗo wonndi e mooɗon Miɗo Nana Miɗo Yi'a"
  20,47,"Aree ka makko, wi'on: \"Menen ko Men Nulaaɓe Joomi maaɗa, accitu wonndude e amen ɓiɗɓe Israa'iila ɓen wata a leptu ɓe, gomɗii men addanii ma Aaya immorde ka Joomi maaɗa, kisiyee on wonii e on jokkuɗo Peewal ngal"
  20,48,"Gomɗii Wahayinaama e amen; wonndema, Lepte ɗen no fawii ka fennuɗo ɗuuri"
  20,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, ko hommbo woni Joomi mooɗon"
  20,50,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Joomi amen, ko On Okkuɗo kala huunde tagu mayre ngun refti O Fewni"
  20,51,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Ko honno gire arane ɗen fewndori"
  20,52,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"ganndal ɗum no ka Joomi am e nder Deftere, Joomi am majjataa O yejjitataa"
  20,53,"On waɗanɗo on leydi ndin weƴƴitaandi, o naadani on e nder mayri laawi, O jippini immorde e kammu ngun ndiyam Men yaltiniri ɗam nooneeji immorde e puɗi sertuɗi"
  20,54,"Ñaamee aynon neemoraaɗi mo'on ɗim. Pellet, no e nder ɗum [ko jaŋtaa ɗoo] Aayeeje fii joomiraa- ɓe hakkillaaji ɗin"
  20,55,"Ko immorde e mayri Men Tagi on, ko e nder mayri Men Ruttata on, ko immorde e mayri kadi Men Yaltinoyta on laawol goo"
  20,56,"Gomɗii Men hollii mo Aayeeje Amen ɗen kala majje, o fenni o salii"
  20,57,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Enee, a aru ka amen fii yo a yaltinir men ka leydi amen mbilaaku maaɗa ngun an Muusaa"
  20,58,"Maa men addane mbilewu yeru maggu, waɗu fodoore hakkunde amen e maaɗa hara men lunndataako nde wanaa an kadi [lunndotoo nde] e nokkuure fotondirnde"
  20,59,"[Muusaa] maaki: fodoore mooɗon nden ko ñalnde saɗɗugol ngol, yo yimɓe ɓen mooɓindire ka walluhaa(fenynyaange)"
  20,60,Fir'awna hucciti o mooɓi pewje makko ɗen refti o ari
  20,61,"Muusaa maakani ɓe: \"On boniraama, wata on fefendo fenaande fawon e Alla sakko O mehira on Lepte, gomɗii sooyii on fefindiiɗo"
  20,62,"Ɓe pooɗondiri fiyaake maɓɓe on hakkunde maɓɓe, ɓe suuɗi cowndi ɗin"
  20,63,"Ɓe wi'i: \"Pellet ɓee ɗiɗo ko mbileeɓe hiɓe faalaa yaltinirnde on ka leydi mon e mbilaaku maɓɓe ngun ɓe itta laawol mon yeruyankeewol ngol"
  20,64,"Mooɓitee pewje mo'on ɗen refti aron ko on lappol, gomɗii malaama hannde on fooluɗo"
  20,65,"Muusaa maaki: \"Ko si tawii ko onon bugotoo maaɗun si ko menen wonata adotooɓe bugaade"
  20,66,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"ko woni, bugee(mbedde), tawi ɓokkoy maɓɓe koy e cawoy maɓɓe koy no wa'itana mo sabu mbilewu maɓɓe ngun woni ko e yahude"
  20,67,Muusaa so'i kulol ka wonkii makko
  20,68,"Men Daali: 'Wata a hulu, pellet ko an woni fooloowo on"
  20,69,"Bugo ko woni kon ka ñaamo maaɗa ɗum moɗay ko ɓe moƴƴini kon, pellet, ko ɓe moƴƴini kon ko pewje mbile bileejo on maletaake nukkuwoo ka o ardi"
  20,70,"Mbileeɓe ɓen werlaa ko ɓe sujjuɓe, ɓe wi'i: \"Men gomɗinii Joomi Haaruuna e Muusaa"
  20,71,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: Eyoo, on gomɗinii mo ko adii mi duŋanaade(sakkitaade) on? Pelet, ko kanko woni mawɗo mo'on on anndinɗo on mbilaaku ngun, mi woondii, maa mi taƴa juuɗe mon ɗen e koyɗe mon ɗen taƴa luutindira, maa mi feta on e julle tama aray anndon ko hommbo e amen ɓuri lepte saɗtuɗe e heddotooɗe"
  20,72,"[Mbileeɓe ɓen] wi'i: \"Men ɓurnataa ma e dow koo ko ari e amen immorde e ɓannganguyeeji, e On Taguɗo men, [an Fir'awna] ñaawu ko ñaawataa kon, pellet, ko ñaawataa ko ka ngurndan aduna ɗoo"
  20,73,"Menen dey, men gomɗinii Joomi amen fii yo o yawtan men goopi amen e kon ko dooluɗaa men e mu'un immorde e mbilewu ngun, ko Alla woni Moƴƴo Heddotooɗo. @Corrected"
  20,74,"Pellet on mo ari ka Joomi mu'un hara ko o bonɗo; haray pellet, no woodani mo Jahannama o maayataa e nder magge o wuurataa kadi"
  20,75,"mo ari ka Makko ko o gomɗinɗo hara gomɗii o golliino moƴƴi ɗin, haray ɓen ɗon no woodani ɓe Darjaaji Toowuɗi ɗin"
  20,76,"Aljannaaji Ñiiɓal no doga e ley majji canɗi ɗin, ko ɓe duumotooɓe nder ton, ko ɗum woni njoɓdi on laɓɓiniiɗo. @Corrected"
  20,77,"Gomɗii Men wahaynii faade e Muusaa roƴidu e jeyaaɓe Am ɓen waɗan ɓe laawol yooru ngol ka maayo joorngol wata a hulu hewtiteede wata a hulu [yoolagol]"
  20,78,"Fir'awna jokkitiri ɓe koneeli makko ɗin, suumi ɓe ka maayo ko suumi ɓe kon"
  20,79,"Fir'awnan majjini yimɓe makko ɓen, o fewnaali [ɓe]"
  20,80,"Ko onon yo ɓiɗɓe Israa'iila gomɗii Men danndiino on e gaño mon on, Men fodi on kadi ka banŋe ñaamo [fello] Tuuri ngon, Men jippini e mooɗon Manna= ɗacce njumri e doobe"
  20,81,"Ñaamee immorde e laaɓuɗi ko Men arsiki on kon, wota on bewu e nder mu'un sakko Tikkere Am nden jippo e mo'on, on mo Tikkere Am jippii e mu'un gomɗii haray o halkike"
  20,82,"Pellet, Min ko Mi heewuɗo Yawtanngol wonannde on tuubuɗo o gomɗini o golli ko moƴƴi refti o feewi"
  20,83,Ko honɗun heñinmaa gaayi yimɓe maa ɓen an Muusaa
  20,84,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ɓeeɗoo, hiɓe iwtiri ɓaawo am, mi heñike ka Maaɗa Joomi fii yo A welto"
  20,85,"[Alla] Daali: \"Pellet, Mennen gomɗii Men jarribike=finninii yimɓe maaɗa ɓen ɓaawo maaɗa, Saamiriiyu majjinii ɓe"
  20,86,"Muusaa ruttii ka yimɓe makko ɓen ko o tikkuɗo suniiɗo; o maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimɓe, enee, Joomi mo'on Fodaali on Fodoore Moƴƴere, kaa ko aadi ndin juutani on? Kaa on faandi nde jippotoo e mo'on Tikkere immorde ka Joomi mooɗon si lunndi ɗon fodoore am nden"
  20,87,"Ɓe wi'i: \"Men lunndaaki fodoore maaɗa nden e sago amen, kono menen men ronndinaama teddeendi e cuɗaaje yimɓe ɓen men werlii ɗe, ko nii Saamiriiyu kadi welirii"
  20,88,"O yaltinani ɓe ɓanndu ngaari marn hito= huunaango, ɓe wi'i: \"Ko ko'ol woni reweteeɗo mon e reweteeɗo Muusaa on, o yejjitu [mo ɗoo]"
  20,89,"Enee, ɓee yi'aali wonndema ruttataako e maɓɓe konngol, ndi maranaa ɓe kadi lorra wonaa fii non [pooɗugol] nafa"
  20,90,"Gomɗii Haaruuna maakaniino ɓe ko adii: \"Ko onon yo yimɓe, pellet, on jarribora kol, pellet, Joomi mooɗon ko Hinnorante On jokkee lam ɗoftoɗon yamiroore am nden"
  20,91,"Ɓe wi'i: \"Men seerataa ko men ñiiɓuɓe e [dewal] makkol haa Muusaa ruttoo e amen"
  20,92,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko an yo Haaruuna, nde yi'unoɗaa ɓe majjii ko haɗumaa"
  20,93,nde jokkitataa mi? Kaa a yeddii yamaruyee am on
  20,94,"[Haaruuna] maaki: \"Ko an yo neene-gooto am, wata a nanngu waare am nden wanaa hoore am nden kadi, min dey, mi hulu wata a wi'u: Mi senndii hakkunde ɓiɗɓe Israa'iila ɓen, mi heɗaaki konngol maaɗa ngol"
  20,95,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko honɗum woni fiyaake maaɗa on an Saamiriiyu"
  20,96,"[Saamiriiyu] wi'i: \"Mi yi'ii ko ɓe yi'aali ɗum, mi nokki nokkannde e batte nulaaɗo on [Jibriila] mi werlii ɗum ko nii cuɗirani lam wonkii am"
  20,97,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Yahu, pellet, no woodanmaa ka ngurndam nde wowlataa wanaa meemondiral, pellet, no woodanmaa kadi Fodoore a lunndataako nde, ndaarii faade e rewteeɗo maa, on mo ñalluɗaa ufinaade e hoore mun, mi woondii mi sunnay mo refti mi jaroo mo ka maayo e jaragol"
  20,98,"Pellet, Reweteeɗo mon On ko Alla, On Mo Reweteeɗo alaa si wanaa Kanko, Ganndal Makko Yaajanii kala huunde"
  20,99,"Ko wano nii Men filloranay maa immorde e kumpital ko feƴƴunoo kon, gomɗii Men addanii ma immorde ka Amen jaŋta"
  20,100,"Mo ɗuurike e mayre pellet, o ronndoto Ñalnde Darngal teddeele [bakkaatu]"
  20,101,"Ko o luttinteeɗo e nder majje, bonanii ɓe donngal Ñalnde Darngal"
  20,102,"Ñalnde wuttoytee ka alaadu Men mooɓa bonɓe ɓen nden Ñalnde ko mbuliiɓe [gite]"
  20,103,"Hiɓe sowndondira hakkunde maɓɓe [ɓe wi'a] on ñiiɓaali si wanaa [balɗe] sappo"
  20,104,"Ko Menen woni Annduɓe ko ɓe wowlata kon, tuma nde koohooɓe maɓɓe e laawol wi'ata: \"On ñiiɓaali si wanaa ñallal"
  20,105,"Hiɓe lanndaade ma fii pelle ɗen, maaku: \"Joomi am jaroto ɗe e jaragol"
  20,106,"O acca [leydi] ndin ko ndi boowal ɓowrungal"
  20,107,A yi'ataa e mayri ooñannde wanaa tintiire
  20,108,"Ko nden Ñalnde ɓe jokkata noddoowo on ko aldaa e selugol mo,, hitooji ɗin yankinanoo Hinnorante On hara a nanataa si wanaa nyuumbaango"
  20,109,"Nden Ñalnde tefoore nden nafataa, si wanaa on mo Hinnorante On sakkiti ɗum O weltori konngol makko"
  20,110,Himo Anndi ko woni kon hedde yeeso maɓɓe e hedde ɓaawo maɓɓe ɓe huɓindortaa ɗum ganndal
  20,111,"Geece ɗen yankinanii Wuuruɗo Dartiiɗo On, gomɗii sooyii on ronndiiɗo tooñe"
  20,112,On mo golli immorde e moƴƴi ɗin hara ko o gomɗinɗo haray o hulaa tooñe wanaa uytaneede kadi
  20,113,Ko nii Men Telliniri nde Alqur'aanaare Aarabuure Men fensiti kadi e nder mayre immorde e kammbaaji ɗin bela-jo'o kamɓe ɓe hulay maa nde fuɗɗanoo ɓe waaju
  20,114,"Alla Lamɗo Goonguɗo On Toowii, wata a heñor Alqur'aanaare nden ko adii nde timmintee e maaɗa wahayu mayre, maaku: \"Joomi ɓeydanam Ganndal"
  20,115,Gomɗii Men ahodiino e Aadama ko adii o yejjiti Men heɓanaali mo pellital
  20,116,"Tuma Nde Men Daalannoo malaa'ikaaɓe ɓen sujjanee Aadama, ɓe sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o salii"
  20,117,"Men Daali: \"Ko an yo Aadama, pellet, ooɗoo ko o gaño maa an e sonnaajo maa on, wata o yaltin on dey ka Aljanna sakko tampaa"
  20,118,"Pellet, no woodanmaa nde a weeletaake nder ton a holataa kadi"
  20,119,"Pellet, an a ɗomɗetaake nde ton e nguletaake kadi"
  20,120,"Seytaane sonwonsini faade e makko; o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Aadama,hara yo mi tinndine e leggal luttineede ngal e laamu ngu follotaako ngun"
  20,121,"Ɓe ñaami e maggal, feeñani ɓe mettefooji maɓɓe ɗin, ɓe naati e suddirgol e dow maɓɓe immorde e kaaki Aljanna on, Aadama yeddi Joomi makko o majji"
  20,122,"Refti Joomi makko Suɓii mo, O Tuubini mo O Fewni [mo]"
  20,123,"O Daali: \"Jippee ton, on fow mo'on, yoga e mo'on ko ayɓe yoga. Si tawii tun aroyii e mo'on immorde e Am Fewnoowo kala jokkuɗo Peewal Am ngal haray o majjataa o malkisataake kadi"
  20,124,"Kala ɗurniiɗo gaayi jaŋtagol lam, haray pellet, no woodani mo ngurndam ɓilluɗam Men mooɓoya mo Ñalnde Darngal ko o bunɗo"
  20,125,"O wi'a: \"Joomi, ko fii honɗum mooɓanɗaa lam ko mi bunɗo, gomɗii mi laatinoke yi'oowo"
  20,126,"O Daala: \"Ko wano nii arunoo e maaɗa Aayeeje Amen ɗen yejjituɗaa ɗe, ko wano nii kadi hannde yejjitirteɗaa"
  20,127,"Ko wano nii Men yoɓirta on fantinɗo hara o gomɗinaa Aayeeje Joomi makko ɗen, pellet, ko Lepte Laakara ɗen ɓuri saɗtude ko ɗen kadi heddotoo"
  20,128,"Kaa hara ɓannganaali ɓe no foti hewde ko Men halki ado maɓɓe immorde e gire? Hiɓe yaha e koɗooli maɓɓe, pellet, no e ɗum Aayeeje wonannde joomiraaɓe hakkillaaji ɓen"
  20,129,"Sinno wonaano Daalol aditii ngol immorde ka Joomi maaɗa [Lepte] ɗen laatotono duumiiɗe e lajal innaangal"
  20,130,"Munño e dow ko ɓe wowlata kon, subuhinor yettugol Joomi maaɗa ko adii ƴellitagol naange ngen e ko adii mutugol magge e ka saa'iiji jemma subuhino e ka seraaji ñallal belajo'o a weltoto"
  20,131,"Wata a yawtin dey gite maa ɗen faade kon ko Men dekmini ɗum nooneeji immorde e maɓɓe, cuɗaari ngurndam aduna fii yo Men jarribor ɓe e ɗum, Arsike Joomi maaɗa on ɓuri moƴƴude ko on kadi heddotoo"
  20,132,"Yamir ɓeynguure maaɗa nden Julde nden monñitoraa e ɗum, Men lanndaaki ma arsike ko Menen arsikaymaa. Battane [moƴƴe] ɗen kadi wonanii hulooɓe Alla ɓen"
  20,133,"Ɓe wi'i: \"Ko hanno ara e amen Aaya immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Enee, hara araali e maɓɓe ɓanngal ko woni kon e ɗeri arani ɗin"
  20,134,"Sinndo Menen Men halkirno ɓe Lepte ko adii ɗum, ɓe wi'ayno: \"Joomi amen, ko hannoo Nualaa e amen Nulaaɗo men jokka Aayeeje Maa ɗen, ko adii nde Men hoyata men hesra"
  20,135,"Maaku: \"Gooto kala [e amen] no habbitii, [onon kadi] habbitee aray anndon ko hommbo woni jom Laawol Focciingol ngol ko hommbo kadi feewi"